OL,3,CVenezuela Fury says she 'ain't
OL,4,Cbothered' by critics after getting
OL,5,Cmarried at 16
OL,7,FVenezuela Fury has said she "ain't
OL,8,Fbothered" about criticism of her
OL,9,Fdecision to get married at the age of
OL,10,F16.
OL,12,FThe teenage reality star, who appears
OL,13,Fin the Netflix series At Home With The
OL,14,FFurys alongside father Tyson Fury,
OL,15,Ftied the knot with boyfriend Noah
OL,16,FPrice, 19, on the Isle of Man in May.
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@IO]
