OL,3,CVenezuela Fury says she 'ain't
OL,4,Cbothered' by critics after getting
OL,5,Cmarried at 16
OL,7,FIn England and Wales you must be at
OL,8,Fleast 18-years-old to marry or form a
OL,9,Fcivil partnership and it is illegal to
OL,10,Fmarry under 18, even with parental
OL,11,Fconsent.
OL,13,FThe legal age for marriage in the Isle
OL,14,Fof Man is 16 with parental consent.
OL,16,FDiscussing how she feels about her
OL,17,Fcritics, she told ITV's This Morning:
OL,18,F"I think, as long it's not my family
OL,19,For my friends, they're the people what
OL,20,Fmatter to me, I ain't bothered.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
