OL,3,CVenezuela Fury says she 'ain't
OL,4,Cbothered' by critics after getting
OL,5,Cmarried at 16
OL,7,F"I don't like people being unkind. I
OL,8,Fdon't agree with spreading badness
OL,9,Fwhere they shouldn't be.
OL,11,F"But yes, I am young, but I found the
OL,12,Fperson I want, and I've carried on
OL,13,Fwith my life. Everyone's got to start
OL,14,Fsomewhere, so I started young."
OL,16,FAsked how she's finding married life,
OL,17,Fshe said: "I'm enjoying it. We've only
OL,18,Fbeen married a month, but everything's
OL,19,Fgoing smoothly.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@_O]yD@KOU
