OL,3,CVenezuela Fury says she 'ain't
OL,4,Cbothered' by critics after getting
OL,5,Cmarried at 16
OL,7,F"I'm learning new things every day.
OL,8,FI'm learning how to cook. We go
OL,9,Feverywhere together. We do everything
OL,10,Ftogether. It's really nice."
OL,12,FBoxer Price told the show he "knew
OL,13,Ffrom the start" that he wanted to
OL,14,Fmarry Venezuela.
OL,16,FHe said: "I didn't want to mess her
OL,17,Fabout, I thought she was perfect.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@\O]tD@^OUuD@OO]xD@JOU
