OL,3,CVenezuela Fury says she 'ain't
OL,4,Cbothered' by critics after getting
OL,5,Cmarried at 16
OL,7,F"I was her first boyfriend, she was
OL,8,Fwife material. When I first seen her,
OL,9,FI thought, yeah, I'm gonna marry that
OL,10,Fgirl one day. And then I made the
OL,11,Fdream come true."
OL,13,FThe family's reality show At Home With
OL,14,FThe Furys follows the heavyweight
OL,15,Fchampion as he exits the ring and
OL,16,Ftries to embrace retirement with his
OL,17,Ffamily including his wife Paris,
OL,18,Ffather John, and their children.
